Text: RE PGEEnron Corp Guarantee Cc Thank you for sending along this draft which reflects the minor changes which are acceptable to PGE Please have the executed Guarantee sent to my attention at Beale Street mail code BL San Francisco CA If you could let me know when you are sending it Id appreciate that Original Message From Tana Jones mailto Sent Monday May PM To Foley Jack Cc Sara Shackleton Subject PGEEnron Corp Guarantee Per our conversation I am attaching a copy of the form of Enron Corp Guaranteee which has been sent today to Enron Corp for signature My direct phone no in case you need to get hold of me is See attached file pacific gas electric guarantydoc
